---
// Technology Section - Showcase approach and innovation
---

<section id="technology" class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block mb-4 px-4 py-2 bg-green/10 rounded-full">
        <span class="text-dark-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide">OUR APPROACH</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-black mb-6">
        Innovative Biotechnology Solutions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-black/70">
        We combine cutting-edge research with practical applications to develop biotechnology solutions that make a real difference.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Features Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-cream p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-dark-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-3">
          Research-Driven
        </h3>
        <p class="text-black/70">
          Our innovations are grounded in rigorous scientific research and validated through comprehensive testing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-cream p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-3">
          Sustainable
        </h3>
        <p class="text-black/70">
          We prioritize environmentally friendly processes and sustainable practices in all our biotechnology solutions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-cream p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-dark-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-3">
          Results-Oriented
        </h3>
        <p class="text-black/70">
          We focus on delivering measurable outcomes and tangible benefits for our clients and partners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Details / Process (Optional - can be expanded) -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-6">
            Our Research Process
          </h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-black/70 mb-6">
            HeartsBio follows a rigorous four-stage research process, from initial discovery through commercial development, ensuring every solution delivers proven results.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-dark-green text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Discovery</h4>
                <p class="text-black/70">Leveraging our proprietary biobank of 10,000+ microbial strains to identify elite candidates with exceptional agricultural potential</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Laboratory Testing</h4>
                <p class="text-black/70">Rigorous evaluation in controlled conditions to measure efficacy, stress response, and ecological compatibility</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-dark-green text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Field Trials</h4>
                <p class="text-black/70">Validation across diverse agricultural ecosystems, documenting real-world performance improvements throughout growing cycles</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-1">Commercial Development</h4>
                <p class="text-black/70">Advanced formulation to optimize stability, application methods, and production scalability while maintaining biological integrity</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Technology visual -->
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="/images/lab-equipment.jpg"
              alt="Advanced biotechnology laboratory"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-dark-green/80 via-dark-green/40 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8">
              <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-dark-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-display font-bold text-dark-green text-lg">10,000+</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-black/70">Microbial Strains</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-black/70">
                  Our proprietary biobank enables rapid innovation
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
